This paper is about neural networks with tree-based sentence encoders, which is a common topic in natural language processing (NLP) research. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the effectiveness of different tree structures, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
